Author: DinosaursAndStarStuf
Text: Uugghhh at my last weight loss job I mentioned something about my blood pressure being weird in earshot of a member (what we called clients) who is also a nurse. She cocked her head and looked at me and then said, "Sometimes if you don't eat enough for a long time that can happen." And I was like fffffffffffuck my life whyyyy.

Author: 3cats_in_atrenchcoat
Text: At least they probably had no idea what you where doing.
